23class errarg {
24 enum { EMPTY, STRING, CHAR, INTEGER, UNSIGNED_INTEGER, DOUBLE } type;
25 union {
26 const char *s;
27 int n;
28 unsigned int u;
29 char c;
30 double d;
31 };
32 public:
33 errarg();
34 errarg(const char *);
35 errarg(char);
36 errarg(unsigned char);
37 errarg(int);
38 errarg(unsigned int);
39 errarg(double);
40 int empty() const;
41 void print() const;
42};
43
44extern errarg empty_errarg;
45
46extern void errprint(const char *,
47 const errarg &arg1 = empty_errarg,
48 const errarg &arg2 = empty_errarg,
49 const errarg &arg3 = empty_errarg);
